name: PetPark
description:
A slow, rotational viewing of a matrix of houses. Or, are they trees? Up to you to determine that, and maybe it doesn’t matter in the end. Uses the Commodore PET graphics device to render an SVG scene. Forever-looping at 12 frames per second.

GIF
320x320
361 frames, 12 fps

by @ecomfort_arts
